Shrink it!
==========

An usefull web tool to shorten or encode your URLS


How to use
---
In order to use Shrink it you have to have [Vertx.io](http://vertx.io/) installed 
and an instance of mongoDB running on the port 27017, on the host 192.168.99.100

Once all is up go to the shrink-it directory and run from the command line: 

```bash
vertx run app.js
```

Then point your browser at 

```bash
http://localhost:8080
```
